data.description: Welcome to this newly renovated 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home that boasts 1,225 square feet of comfortable living space. This charming house has been updated with modern finishes and is ready for you to move in. The 1-year-old HVAC system ensures that you'll be comfortable all year round. The brand-new carport provides convenient covered parking, protecting your vehicle from the elements. Inside, the kitchen has been updated with new appliances, stylish countertops, and ample cabinet space for storage. The original hardwood floors have been lovingly restored and custom stained, providing a unique and timeless look throughout the home. All three bedrooms are spacious and comfortable, perfect for relaxing after a long day. This home is located in an ideal location close to great schools, making it perfect for families. Don't miss this opportunity to make this stunning home your own!
